              </svg>
            </span>
            ian.p.rosado@gmail.com
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ianrosado/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-stone-700 hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors group">
